timeline.body:
This method can be written as a single loop.

```java
for(int i = 0; i < items.length; i++){
    int index = (i + takeRotation) % items.length;
    if(items[index] > 0){
        items[index] --;
        total --;
        takeRotation = (index + 1) % items.length;
        return content.item(i);
    }
}
```

